PortSystem          1.0
PortGroup           cargo   1.0
PortGroup           github  1.0

github.setup        jj-vcs jj 0.39.0 v
github.tarball_from archive
name                jujutsu
revision            0

description         A Git-compatible DVCS that is both simple and powerful

long_description    \
    Jujutsu is a Git-compatible DVCS. It combines features from Git (data \
    model, speed), Mercurial (anonymous branching, simple CLI free from \"the \
    index\", revsets, powerful history-rewriting), and Pijul/Darcs \
    (first-class conflicts), with features not found in most of them \
    (working-copy-as-a-commit, undo functionality, automatic rebase, safe \
    replication via rsync, Dropbox, or distributed file system). The \
    command-line tool is called jj for now because it\'s easy to type and \
    easy to replace (rare in English). The project is called \"Jujutsu\" \
    because it matches \"jj\".

categories          devel
